# MPU — future enhancements knowledge

When planning or implementing new features for Morris PeopleSoft Utilities:

1. Read **`docs/findings/future-enhancements.md`** (canonical BA + developer backlog).
2. Prefer **P1** items (Field Inspector copy, richer Page Info, Favorites categories/filter, Fluid inspect, Trace presets) unless the user specifies otherwise.
3. Agent plan stub: **`.cursor/plans/future-enhancements.md`**.
4. Still obey compliance rules: no credentials/Quick Logins, no telemetry, `chrome.storage.local` only, opt-in host allowlist.
5. After shipping a backlog item, mark it done in the findings doc Capture log / strike through the ID row, and mention it in CHANGELOG + wiki use cases when user-visible.
